displayName: Medicine Town Medishina, Home of Pharmacist Santana

parameters: Pharmacist Santana: Damn it, why isn't it working...!
Pharmacist Santana: Did you come from Oros!?
Clea: Yes, I came from the Adventurer's Guild.

Mage Relm: You're lucky! I'm a prodigy from the prestigious
Magic Academy!

Pharmacist Santana: Magic Academy...! Damn it, I went
through the trouble of requesting it in Oros!

Pharmacist Santana: There's a certain reputation that comes
with being a pharmacist, so I avoided requesting from the
Magic Academy...
Clea: Relm-san, do you have any knowledge of pharmacy?

Mage Relm: There's nothing I can't do, but I'm primarily an
expert in magical tomes...

Pharmacist Santana: P-Please, I'm begging you! You're the
great genius from the Magic Academy, right!?

Mage Relm: G-Got it... I-I understand! I'll take care of
the pharmacy work for you!
Mage Relm: Now, please hand over your research results!

Pharmacist Santana: I appreciate your kindness! I have made
some progress in my research!

Mage Relm: Of course! Now, let's complete the recipe at the
Magic Academy.
Pharmacist Santana: I'm counting on you guys, please!

Mage Relm: This is the recipe. Please confirm it as the
pharmacist.

Pharmacist Santana: This is... amazing! I see, so I just
need to neutralize it with a different poisonous herb!

Pharmacist Santana: Hahaha, as expected of the academy's
great genius!

Mage Relm: You can praise me more, you know! Well, it's a
piece of cake for me, though!

Pharmacist Santana: This is your reward. If you need
anything else, feel free to consult with me.

Pharmacist Santana: I'll continue to ask for your help with
troublesome medicine that I can't handle myself!
